tissueExpression.summary: Granular cytoplasmic expression in selected tissues.

subcellularLocation.summary: Mainly localized to the mitochondria. In addition localized to the nucleus.

tissueExpression.summary: Strong granular cytoplasmic positivity was observed in kidney and prostate. Other glandular cells displayed weak cytoplasmic staining. Remaining normal tissues were in general negative.
Distinct granular cytoplasmic positivity was found in most prostate cancers and in few liver cancers. Remaining malignant tissues were in general negative.
